{"tid":156164,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[真誠賣香港］有無人想追擊民主黨？","createTime":"2017-03-14T14:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T14:05:22.000Z","uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"550ec086d8f53ca5eae1de9428a04966343f875b","tid":156164,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T14:00:29.000Z","msg":"而家係泛民開恊調大會既時候<br />\n如果而家搞民主黨<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">好大機會令其他黨派搶佔民主黨地盤<br />\n亦有機會令本土派執雞</span><br />\n當然最緊要係令民主黨既地盤縮細<br />\n而家係搞死民主黨既時機<br />\n大家點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家恊調機制入面<br />\n泛民如果一個區多個一個人出選<br />\n會勸退是但一個<br />\n如果係恊調當中泛民有意出選既人突然爆左d黑材料出黎<br />\n咁個條友係恊調機制中已經無左個話語權<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁搞死民主黨,得益既並唔係保皇<br />\n而係其他泛民/本土</span>可以打到個區<br />\n<br />\n基本上係上一次區選民主黨有出選既區<br />\n今次民主黨係恊調時都有落名落去<br />\n而人都基本上係個一個（除非退休/退黨）<br />\n<br />\n可以做既野有好多，但最緊要係可以組到一班人去做野<br />\n<br />\nE.g起個d人既底，搵黑材料攻擊<br />\n<br />\n開個telegram gp<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1JhsE9njVMTgJxcuWGy5BL7pQ4q5QYNJcv0ve8fUC7MM/prefill\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1JhsE9njVMTgJxcuWGy5BL7pQ4q5QYNJcv0ve8fUC7MM%2Fprefill&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0e873f82\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1JhsE9njVMTgJxcuWGy5BL7pQ4q5QYNJcv0ve8fUC7MM/prefill</a><br />\n有興趣一齊搞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重伸一句：而家搞民主黨，係最好時機，又唔會影響大局既時間"},{"pid":"46ab5b8a76d2219fb6b6aad8d00fe8dcf71e3a9c","tid":156164,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T14:02:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86412f87db79215c5b7d0ef0ca1a174890f978c9","tid":156164,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T14:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d334d2ac29803624b0690067db51742aee1b89d","tid":156164,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T14:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}